%p= "Hi #{@invitation[:first_name]},"

- unless @invitation[:specially]

  %p I’ve looked at your portfolio and am a big fan of your work.

- else

  %p= "I’ve looked at your portfolio and am a big fan of your work, especially #{@invitation[:specially]}."


%p My name is Victor, co-founder of Pictorical. Nice to meet you. Pictorical publishes the world’s greatest stories, illustrated by emerging artists all over the world—just like you.

%p I’d like to invite you to join us. As part of Pictorical, you will be published worldwide and earn half of the profits from the sale of your books.

%p
  %b What's next?

%p
  To start illustrating your first story, go to
  = link_to "Pictorical's publishing tool", @url
  and sign up with your email address,
  = "#{@invitation[:email]}."

%p
  If you have any questions, you can ask us at
  = "#{link_to 'artists@pictorical.com', 'mailto:artists@pictorical.com'}.".html_safe

%p Looking forward to having you on board,

%p Best,

%p Victor, co-founder of Pictorical

%p
  PS: In case you are wondering, you received this email because you sent us your portfolio on
  = link_to "Pictorical's website", "http://artists.pictorical.com"